{"subject":"Geography","year":2011,"question":"The main message of the IPCC reports is that:","options":[\"Climate change is real and human‑induced\",\"Climate change is not occurring\",\"Human activity has no impact\",\"The Earth is cooling\"],"correctIndex":0,"explanation":"IPCC concluded that climate change is unequivocal and human‑caused."},
{"subject":"Geography","year":2012,"question":"The term \"blue economy\" refers to:","options":[\"Sustainable use of ocean resources for economic growth\",\"Environmentally friendly industries\",\"Green energy\",\"Non‑renewable resource use\"],"correctIndex":0,"explanation":"Blue economy is about ocean sustainability."},
