{"subject":"Geography","year":2014,"question":"The concept of \"green economy\" emphasises:","options":[\"Low‑carbon, resource‑efficient, and socially inclusive development\",\"High carbon, high resource use\",\"Exclusive development\",\"Capital‑intensive growth\"],"correctIndex":0,"explanation":"Green economy is sustainable and inclusive."},
