{"subject":"Geography","year":2000,"question":"The atmosphere is divided into layers; the lowest layer is the:","options":[\"Troposphere\",\"Stratosphere\",\"Mesosphere\",\"Thermosphere\"],"correctIndex":0,"explanation":"The troposphere is the lowest layer (0‑12 km)."},
