{"subject":"Geography","year":2004,"question":"Climate is the:","options":[\"Long‑term average weather\",\"Short‑term atmospheric conditions\",\"Current temperature\",\"Forecast\"],"correctIndex":0,"explanation":"Climate is the average weather over 30+ years."},
{"subject":"Geography","year":2005,"question":"The main elements of weather are:","options":[\"Temperature, precipitation, wind, humidity, pressure\",\"Only temperature and rainfall\",\"Only wind and pressure\",\"Only humidity and clouds\"],"correctIndex":0,"explanation":"These are the key weather elements."},
